ria]]\n*** Political party: [[Bavaria Party]] (EFA member)<ref>''[https://bayernpartei.de/satzung/ Satzung der Bayernpartei]'', 30. October 2011, from: ''bayernpartei.de'', 28 August 2018</ref>\n\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Sorbs.svg}} [[Lusatia]]\n* People: [[Sorbs]]\n** Proposed state: {{flagicon image|Flag of Sorbs.svg}} [[Lusatia]]\n*** Political party: [[Lusatian Alliance]]\n\n;Autonomist movements\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Bavaria (state).svg}} [[Bavaria]]\n* People: [[Bavarians]]\n** Proposed autonomous area: [[Bavaria]]\n*** Political party: [[Bavaria Party]] (EFA member)<ref>''[https://bayernpartei.de/satzung/ Satzung der Bayernpartei]'', 30. October 2011, from: ''bayernpartei.de'', 28 August 2018</ref>, [[Christian Social Union in Bavaria]]\n\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Sorbs.svg}} [[Lusatia]]\n* People: [[Sorbs]]\n** Proposed autonomous area: [[Lusatia]]\n*** Political party: [[Lusatian Alliance]]\n\n{{main|Rhenish nationalism}}\n{{flagicon image|Flag of North Rhine-Westphalia.svg}} [[Rhineland]]\n* People: [[Rhineland|Rhinelanders]]\n** Proposed autonomous area: [[Rhineland]]\n*** Movement: [[Rhenish nationalism]]\n\n{{main|Swabian nationalism}}\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg (state, lesser arms).svg}} [[Swabia]]\n* People: [[Swabians]]\n** Proposed autonomous area: [[Swabia]]\n*** Movement: [[Swabian nationalism]]\n\n==Italy==\n{{Main|Secession in Italy}}\n{{See|Italian unification}}\n\n\n{{Main|Friulian Front}}\n[[File:Italian-unification.gif|thumb|250px|[[Italian unification]]]]\n\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Friuli-Venezia Giulia.svg}} [[Friuli-Venezia Giulia]]\n\n* People: [[Friulian people|Friulians]]\n** Proposed state: {{flagicon image|Bandiere dal Fri\u00fbl.svg}} [[Friuli]]\n*** Political parties: \n**** Secessionist parties: [[Res Publica Furlane-Parlament Furlan]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.corriere.it/cronache/14_luglio_27/web-referendum-indipendenza-friuli-51e0f6c8-15b3-11e4-bcb3-09a23244c28e.shtml|title=Dopo il Veneto prova 