ars]]\n**Militant organisation: [[All-Tatar Public Center]]\n***Advocacy groups: The Union of Tatar Youth, Tatar Patriotic Front Altyn Urda, Tatar Social Center\n***Government in exile: Tatar Government in Exile\n***Organization: [[Ittifaq Party]]\n**Proposed state: {{flagicon image|Tatar Nationalist Flag.svg}} [[Tatarstan]]\n\n{{flag|Udmurtia}}<ref>{{Citation | contribution = POHC | contribution-url = http://ronsslav.com/v-udmurtiya-poyavilas-organizatsiya-regionalnyh-separatistov/ | last1 = | last2 = | title = \u0412 \u0423\u0434\u043c\u0443\u0440\u0442\u0438\u044f \u043f\u043e\u044f\u0432\u0438\u043b\u0430\u0441\u044c \u043e\u0440\u0433\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0437\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f \u0440\u0435\u0433\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u0441\u0435\u043f\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0432}}</ref>\n*People: [[Udmurts]]\n**Proposed state: {{flag|Udmurtia}}\n***Movement: Congress of the Peoples of Udmurtia\n***Advocacy groups:[[Udmurt Kenesh]], [[Udmurt National Centre]], [[Udmurt National Progress]], [[Odmort]]\n***Political parties: [[Udmurt Republican National Party]], [[Udmurt National Progress]]\n\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Bashkortostan.svg}} [[Bashkortostan]]<ref name=\"politico\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.politico.com/magazine/story/2019/08/03/russia-separatism-vladimir-putin-227498|title=The Best Way to Deal With Russia: Wait for It to Implode|last=Eltsov|first=Peter|date=3 August 2019|website=Politico|language=en-US|access-date=9 October 2019}}</ref>\n*People: [[Bashkirs|Bashkir]]\n**Advocacy groups: Bashkort Public Organization, Bashkir Human Rights Movement, Council of Aksakals of Bashkortostan, Bashkir Social Movement\n***Political party: The Heavenly Wolf\n**Proposed state: {{flagicon image|Flag of Bashkurdistan.svg}} [[Bashkortostan]]\n\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Chuvashia.svg}} [[Chuvashia]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://eadaily.com/ru/news/2016/01/19/toskoy-po-suverenitetu-iz-chuvashii-vdohnovilis-vragi-rossii-na-u